  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01124:5b3f79c94552]]\n本轮新增七个不可缩水原子：\n\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01125:06395308c32d]]：MODEL_GENERATED 不能成为正向 action/Voice/真人范文；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01126:525646c26c31]]：共享标题 false route；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01127:fa78b9b61b0c]]：逻辑 include prior 只补同场景弱证据；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01128:2a76d0046d75]]：Profile set/entry/metadata claims 越权；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01129:e274684e094d]]：逐 unit、跨场景 Voice hash；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01130:a976a99ace07]]：当前 policy、冻结 source、include、metadata 独立重建；\n- [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01131:5ca47f2c8403]]：fresh case Profile 可见、样本文本不泄漏、同场景分块漂移。\n\n固定 requirements 为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01132:dc1299e283e2]]，contract 为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01133:d58f6ddaf8e0]]。无 evidence manifest 的正式审计结果\n仍是：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01134:c4fbd67e2f96]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01135:89d1cd56461f]]、\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01136:e3599dfd782e]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01137:d310d8a2bf00]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01138:2d516198e529]]、exit 2。这里的 PASS 只属于“空证据被\n诚实识别”，不是生成模型通过。\n\n",
